# N0 -> Number of incident photons/mm2
# n -> Number of the detector cells
# cellSize -> Size of the edge of the detector cell in mm
# noduleSize -> Diameter of the nodule in mm 
# noduleContrast -> Nodule contrast in %

N0= 4000000
n= 100*100   # Suppose a square shape detector
cellSize= 0.1
